    "Examples and testsIn the present research, we presents six categories of examples for the evaluation of the performance of different LLM.",
    "The list of examples is summarized in Table 2, related to knowledge of Exudyn and the creation of basic dynamic and multibody systems.",
    "All examples are tested and evaluated with several LLM, using GPT-3.5, GPT-4, Bard (PaLM-2), and LLaMA-2, 6 see Table 1 for details.",
    "GPT-3.5 and GPT-4 are accessed using ChatGPT.Note that the maximum number of tokens are crucial for our tests, as they limit the input as well as the output text.",
    "In order to be processed more efficiently, LLM convert text into tokens, often with approximately 32 000 different tokens."
